OL,3,C'Extensive' searches ongoing for
OL,4,Cmissing teen not seen for a week
OL,6,FPolice are carrying out extensive
OL,7,Fsearches to try and find a 14-year-old
OL,8,Ffrom Barnstaple who has been missing
OL,9,Ffor almost a week.
OL,11,FTaylor Charlton was last seen at
OL,12,Faround 10.40pm on Friday 8 May near a
OL,13,FTesco store in the Seven Brethren
OL,14,Farea, Devon and Cornwall Police have
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
