CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779185247
OL,3,C'Extensive' searches ongoing for
OL,4,Cmissing teen not seen for a week
OL,6,FThe teenager is around 5ft 8in tall,
OL,7,Fof muscular build, with dark brown
OL,8,Fhair and a moustache and was last seen
OL,9,Fwearing a bright blue fitted top,
OL,10,Fjeans and bright blue Nike shoes,
OL,11,Fofficers added.
OL,13,FPolice have asked people not to fly
OL,14,Fdrones in an attempt to help, adding
OL,15,Fthat it could hinder the search and
OL,16,Fresult in prosecution.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
