PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779185247
OL,3,C'Extensive' searches ongoing for
OL,4,Cmissing teen not seen for a week
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police Inspector
OL,7,FAndy Wills said: "A significant
OL,8,Finvestigation is ongoing, and
OL,9,Fdetectives are keeping all options
OL,10,Fopen in our efforts to find Taylor.
OL,12,F"Today, as we continue searching for
OL,13,FTaylor, people in the community will
OL,14,Fcontinue to see activity across the
OL,15,FBarnstaple area involving emergency
OL,16,Fservices and volunteer search teams.
OL,18,F"We would kindly ask members of the
OL,19,Fpublic not to fly drones in the area
OL,20,Fwhile this search is ongoing.
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779185247
OL,3,C'Extensive' searches ongoing for
OL,4,Cmissing teen not seen for a week
OL,6,F"Drone flights are prohibited in the
OL,7,Fvicinity of the ongoing emergency
OL,8,Fservice incident until further notice.
OL,9,FThe use of drones in or near the
OL,10,Flocation poses a significant risk to
OL,11,Fthe safety of emergency personnel and
OL,12,Fcould hinder the investigation.
OL,14,F"We know how much people want to help,
OL,15,Fif you are out looking, please take
OL,16,Fcare and avoid putting yourself at
OL,17,Frisk, including entering unsafe
OL,18,Fbuildings or going near the water.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779185247
OL,3,C'Extensive' searches ongoing for
OL,4,Cmissing teen not seen for a week
OL,6,F"If you become aware of an area that
OL,7,Fyou think may be relevant, please pass
OL,8,Fthis information on to us.
OL,10,F"We also ask people to avoid sharing
OL,11,Fspeculation on social media. We
OL,12,Funderstand people want to help;
OL,13,Fhowever unconfirmed information can
OL,14,Fsometimes make enquiries more
OL,15,Fchallenging. If you have any
OL,16,Finformation that could assist, please
OL,17,Freport it directly to police.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779185247
OL,3,C'Extensive' searches ongoing for
OL,4,Cmissing teen not seen for a week
OL,6,F"I would like to sincerely thank
OL,7,Feveryone who has supported the search
OL,8,Fso far and those who have already
OL,9,Fshared information with us.
OL,11,F"Every detail, no matter how small,
OL,12,Fhelps us build a clearer picture and
OL,13,Ffocus our efforts. Please continue to
OL,14,Fget in touch if you have anything that
OL,15,Fmay assist, including dash-cam,
OL,16,Fdoorbell or CCTV footage.
OL,18,F"Specialist police teams will continue
OL,19,Fto be involved in today's searches,
OL,20,Fincluding dive teams and trained
OL,21,Fsearch officers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
